_sText:
I was tired of this sitting in my maps folder. Worked on for like 8 months on and off. 11 stages, mostly involving pre-speed or dumb triggers that barely function as intended. If you don't like fun then you'll enjoy this map.

Difficulty: Literally barely possible, if possible at all
Length (Perfect Run): 1 to 2 minutes
Length (Casual): At least 5 minutes, maybe even 10+ minutes.

I'm fairly certain it is not even possible, but maybe somebody out there will finish it.

Update: renamed to bhop_challenging because bhop_challenge was already taken.
